The hive ships will be in range
of the satellite in forty nine hours.

57
00:02:38,963 --> 00:02:41,746
我们需要充分利用这其中的每一秒钟
We're gonna need every last second,
of that time.

58
00:02:41,886 --> 00:02:43,834
还有什么问题么?
Questions?

59
00:02:46,304 --> 00:02:48,287
