Ok, let's get on it.

60
00:02:49,435 --> 00:02:51,176
Rodney
Well Rodney.

61
00:02:51,280 --> 00:02:55,942
我并不是想给你增加压力
不过此时此刻
Don't mean to put any undue pressure,
but at this moment,

62
00:02:56,080 --> 00:03:02,100
那个卫星是唯一可以在幽灵和亚特兰蒂斯之间
起抵抗作用的东西了
that satellite is the only thing standing
between the Wraith and Atlantis.

63
00:03:02,239 --> 00:03:04,222
不要压力过大
No undue pressure?

64
00:04:00,572 --> 00:04:06,581
星际之门之亚特兰蒂斯
第一季第19集 围攻 第一部分
StarGate Atlantis
1x19 - The Siege

