我看你有些太心急了
I'm looking for something
a little more enthusiastic, than fine.

67
00:04:16,519 --> 00:04:18,781
我已经准备好回去执行任务了
I'm ready to be put back
on active duty.

68
00:04:18,885 --> 00:04:20,590
我知道你是这样想的
