I see no further reason she should be
kept here under medical supervision.

72
00:04:28,870 --> 00:04:32,037
好吧, 你可以回去参加任务了
Alright, you're back on active duty.

73
00:04:41,326 --> 00:04:42,787
我认为我自己可以处理这个!
I think I can handle this alone!

74
00:04:42,891 --> 00:04:44,945
你没有别的事要去做的么?
Isn't there something better
you should be doing?

75
00:04:45,083 --> 00:04:46,127
我认为我应该去
I think I should go.

76
00:04:46,267 --> 00:04:47,066
是的, 我同意
Yes, I agree.

77
00:04:47,206 --> 00:04:47,902
走吧!
Go!

78
00:04:48,040 --> 00:04:49,398
我的意思是, 参加这次任务
I mean, on the mission.

79
00:04:49,537 --> 00:04:50,650
为什么?
Why?

80
00:04:50,789 --> 00:04:53,295
