I take it back.

93
00:05:12,603 --> 00:05:13,265
别!
No!

94
00:05:13,404 --> 00:05:13,751
抱歉!
不要!
Sorry!
Nope!

95
00:05:13,891 --> 00:05:16,083
你无法收回刚才所说的话, 因为你已经承认了
我比你更加聪明
You can't take it back, because you've just
admitted that I am smarter than you are.

96
00:05:16,223 --> 00:05:17,266
我并没有承认这一点!
I admitted no such thing!

97
00:05:17,371 --> 00:05:19,388
