111
00:06:01,556 --> 00:06:03,296
是的
Yes they are.

112
00:06:03,435 --> 00:06:05,731
M4H-212如何?
How about M4H-212?

113
00:06:05,835 --> 00:06:07,297
有Genii的间谍在上面活动
Crawling with Genii spies.

114
