00:27:11,560 --> 00:27:13,509
我们已经就位了, 先生
We're in position sir.

481
00:27:13,891 --> 00:27:18,762
好的, Miller
我要你打开通风孔
Ok Miller. I want you to vent
the atmosphere and disengage

482
00:27:18,901 --> 00:27:23,041
并且解除后部舱室的人工重力
the artificial gravity
in the rear compartment.

483
00:27:28,991 --> 00:27:31,113
