We can send secure messages,
there's no reason he can't.

594
00:36:00,221 --> 00:36:03,526
也许我可以试着跟它建立连接
Maybe I can try and connect
with him.

595
00:36:04,326 --> 00:36:06,275
我不这样认为
I don't think so.

596
00:36:08,605 --> 00:36:12,363
如果阿尔法站点已经被发现了, 少校
If the Alpha Site has been
compromised Major,

597
00:36:12,502 --> 00:36:14,416
我们需要知道
we need to know.

598
00:36:20,818 --> 00:36:22,975
好吧, 看看你能做些什么
Ok, see what you can do.

599
00:36:47,085 --> 00:36:52,548
从手动模式切换到自动开火模式
就绪!
Switching over from manual
to automatic firing mode. Stand by!

600
00:36:54,705 --> 00:36:56,688
就绪
Standing by.

601
00:37:15,858 --> 00:37:17,876
我们已经干掉一艘了!
We have a kill!

602
00:37:20,903 --> 00:37:22,817
我们收到了, Rodney
We copy that, Rodney.

603
00:37:22,956 --> 00:37:24,905
打下了一艘, 还有两艘
One down, two to go.

604
00:37:32,141 --> 00:37:34,437
你在做什么, 人类?
What are you doing, human?

605
00:37:39,343 --> 00:37:42,404
你正在试图进入我的意识
You're trying to get inside my mind.

606
00:37:47,832 --> 00:37:49,815
允许我!
Allow me!

607
00:37:55,346 --> 00:37:58,583
Teyla? 停下来!
你在做什么?
Teyla? Stop it!
What are you doing?

608
00:38:02,236 --> 00:38:04,184
你还好吧?
Are you ok?

609
00:38:07,142 --> 00:38:08,811
我身上的创伤会自动恢复
My wounds will heal.

610
00:38:08,915 --> 00:38:10,968
是的, 不过要多久?
Yeah, but for how long?

611
00:38:14,552 --> 00:38:18,519
我要知道你对这个城市做了些什么
I need to know what
you've done to this city.

612
00:38:20,849 --> 00:38:26,172
听着Bob, 不管怎样
我都可以轻松的杀死你
Listen Bob. I have no problem
with killing you, whatsoever.

613
00:38:35,357 --> 00:38:38,280
快点, 快点
再次出击啊!
Come on, come on.
Hit em again!

614
00:38:38,419 --> 00:38:39,811
我们有问题了!
We have a problem!

615
00:38:39,950 --> 00:38:41,898
什么, 什么问题?
What, what problem?

616
00:38:43,046 --> 00:38:47,083
看起来好像是
我们改线之后的发送器过载了
It looks like the sender
we rerouted has overloaded.

617
00:38:47,221 --> 00:38:51,570
武器不能再次发射了
我正试图寻找其它的方法
The weapon can't fire again.
I'm trying to find another pathway.

618
00:38:51,709 --> 00:38:52,927
我们就回来接你
We're heading back in to pick you up.

619
00:38:53,031 --> 00:38:54,319
呆在原地别动!
Stay exactly where you are!

620
00:38:54,423 --> 00:38:56,128
我们已经隐形了, 它们不会看到我们的!
Look, we're cloaked,
they won't see us!

621
00:38:56,268 --> 00:39:00,477
没有时间了
快点离开这里!
There's no time,
just get the hell out of here!

622
00:39:04,095 --> 00:39:05,522
我很抱歉!
I'm sorry!

623
00:39:05,626 --> 00:39:08,166
把我们带回到卫星那里去
Get us back to that satellite.

624
00:39:18,047 --> 00:39:19,996
噢, 天哪!
Oh God!

625
00:39:22,118 --> 00:39:27,685
我不是在跟你浪费时间, Bob!
你到底对这个基地采取了破坏行动没有?
I'm not screwing around Bob!
Did you sabotage this base or not?

626
00:39:31,650 --> 00:39:36,765
那些从你身上取食的幽灵
将会知道你对我所做的一切
Those who feed upon you,
will know what you've done to me.

627
00:39:40,801 --> 00:39:42,540
是的, 那我们来看看吧
Yeah, we'll see.

628
00:39:42,680 --> 00:39:45,115
长官! 我想我们也许有点过头了
Sir! I think maybe we've gone a bit too far.

629
00:39:45,219 --> 00:39:47,446
我认为我们还做得不够
I don't think we've gone far enough.

630
00:39:47,585 --> 00:39:52,282
亚特兰蒂斯, 我是McKay!
我们已经失去了卫星!
Atlantis, this is McKay!
We have lost the satellite!

631
00:39:56,213 --> 00:39:58,128
你们有没有打下更多的飞船?
Did you manage to take
out any more ships?

632
00:39:58,266 --> 00:40:02,371
没有, 另外两艘飞船都完好无损
Negative. The two other
hive ships are intact.

633
00:40:02,894 --> 00:40:07,312
Elizabeth, Peter Grodin
当时正在卫星上
Elizabeth, Peter Grodin
was aboard the satellite.

634
00:40:10,757 --> 00:40:14,862
明白
另外两艘是什么状态?
Understood.
What's the status of the other two?

635
00:40:14,966 --> 00:40:17,124
它们没有继续靠近了
They're not coming any closer.

636
00:40:17,262 --> 00:40:19,732
看起来好像它们在重新考虑它们的计划
Looks like they're rethinking
their plans.

637
00:40:19,872 --> 00:40:22,517
至少来说, 他为我们带来更多的时间
At the very least,
he's bought us some time.

638
00:40:22,655 --> 00:40:27,770
你在那儿也做不了什么了, Rodney
返回亚特兰蒂斯吧
You can't do anymore out there Rodney.
Return to Atlantis.

639
00:40:33,650 --> 00:40:35,633
正回来
On our way

640
00:40:40,852 --> 00:40:42,799
我要对整个城市讲话
Put me on city wide.

641
00:40:46,627 --> 00:40:51,393
各位请注意
我是Weir博士
May I have your attention please.
This is Doctor Weir.

642
