Therefore, we must begin
our evacuation plans.

645
00:41:02,770 --> 00:41:08,372
我希望我能够告诉你们
这是一场我们可以打赢的战争
I wish I could tell you all that this
is a fight that we will win,

646
00:41:08,476 --> 00:41:10,251
可是我做不到
but I can't do that.

647
00:41:10,389 --> 00:41:16,860
