I can tell you this.

649
00:41:21,697 --> 00:41:26,777
直到现在为止
你们大家都已经实现了非凡的成就
Up till now, you all have accomplished
extraordinary things,

650
00:41:26,881 --> 00:41:31,995
并且我确信
即使是面对无法确定的未来
and I believe that even in
the face of an uncertain future,

651
00:41:32,100 --> 00:41:37,771
只要我们团结在一起
